{"tw": {"2846220": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "姐姐大人同居中。～唯奈濃情蜜意的全肯定～", "steam_appid": 2846220, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3600610], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/79e6785449adf7a4d178b47c413f83c4.poster.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/79e6785449adf7a4d178b47c413f83c4.webm?t=1774841385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前往公司上班、工作結束就回家睡覺。在這種生活裡漸漸淡心的你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到有一天——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「――歡迎回家！」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有這麼一句溫柔的聲音迎接了你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是不會結束的、「與姐姐一起」的日子――。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/b6fbebd83da1d093a14f65526177a413.webp?t=1774841385\" width=300 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/2a49efd47e7bd1c60995fa2c227bc200.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯奈 (CV沢野ぽぷら)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是比你年長的親戚。從小就住在你附近。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你就職之前，她就像真正的姐姐一樣照顧著你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很有包容力、很有母性。為了你可以做任何事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非常理解男性的生理需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/4d7bd9b09bbce287f030fa947357e16c.webp?t=1774841385\" width=300 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/83ed6bb4270f162b58da52a4f2ca230e.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這個遊戲是與女主人公姐姐一起，黏在一起生活的互動式遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與姐姐抱在一起，接吻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >給你體驗膝枕，掏耳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一張床上一起睡覺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在休息日裡一起出門，去水族館約會。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以一直享受「與甜蜜蜜姐姐的純度100%恩愛」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/57b7dfca281aa68c7aaafa7c19bc7585.webp?t=1774841385\" width=300 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/a3341fdfce9dfe14ca94cfbf81d34e10.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >姐姐十分瞭解男性生理上的知識，在H上也十分的積極！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手交、授乳手交、乳交、口交、正常位、後入、騎乘位、等等……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在H場景裡，由正統文學類的描寫+場景臺詞，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還搭載有可以自己操作的命令選擇型的H！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至滿足一定條件後還能進行COS H，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >姐姐的臺詞也隨著衣服的更換選擇不同的言語……♪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/1fb164d292560bf0970a44b7f7db77eb.webp?t=1774841385\" width=300 height=60 /></span>這個遊戲沒有結局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與姐姐成為戀人關係，加深彼此的關係也行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >僅僅進行柏拉圖式的關係