/li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 3 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2+ GHz Processor<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL ES 2.0 hardware driver support required for WebGL acceleration. (AMD Catalyst 10.9, nVidia 358.50)<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 6 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["ボウサバG"], "publishers": ["072 Project", "072 News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 31000, "final": 31000, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 310"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 2 月 21 日"}}}}, "us": {"2846220": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Together with Oneesan~Yuina's Sweet Encouragement~", "steam_appid": 2846220, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3600610], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/79e6785449adf7a4d178b47c413f83c4.poster.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/79e6785449adf7a4d178b47c413f83c4.webm?t=1774841385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You go to work, come home, and just sleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're living those exhausting days that wear your soul down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one day...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;――Welcome home!&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That gentle voice welcomes you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the never-ending &quot;Days with My Sister&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/db421b0ec847d67241fa2f6d9b12b2ae.webp?t=1774841385\" width=371 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/396c1b6610175442f92c8f1a94c671bd.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yuina (CV沢野ぽぷら)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cousin. She has lived near you since you were little and has taken care of you like a real sister until you got a job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She's extremely understanding and maternal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She'll do anything for you if it's for your sake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She has a deep understanding of male physiology (=sexual desire).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/fa06cab85761ebaa746514092e1a34c8.webp?t=1774841385\" width=371 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/76b440d1e17aa4280f016de2158a3d37.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a communication game where you spend time &quot;just&quot; indulging in affectionate moments with the heroine, your older sister.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can hug your sister tightly, kiss her repeatedly, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >have her give you a knee pillow, and clean your ears. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also sleep together in one bed, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or go on outings together, like aquarium dates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can continue enjoying &quot;sweet, 100% pure affection with your sister&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/aa8b3adc479160c986a0ef8b6f4f0b88.webp?t=1774841385\" width=371 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/a3341fdfce9dfe14ca94cfbf81d34e10.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your sister is very understanding of male physiology, so she actively engages in intimate moments!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handjobs, Nursing Handjobs, Titjobs, Blowjobs, Missionary, Doggy Style, Cowgirl, and more....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to conventional scenes with text and dialogue, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >there's also a command selection H system where you can control the intimate actions yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Furthermore, by meeting certain conditions, you can engage in cosplay H scenes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your sister's dialogue also changes to match the costume she's wearing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/4f11ce16ce2ca9b897cfda0b61536884.webp?t=1774841385\" width=371 height=60 /></span>There are no endings in this game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can either become lovers with your sister and deepen your relationship or simply continue being good friends platonically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the sweet life with your sister that continues endlessly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/b7fff6825a2e984e45e0c621dff80d97.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=69 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ilustrations by Kaisen Chuui</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planning/Scenario by 4D Megane</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Produced by Bousaba G</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/79e6785449adf7a4d178b47c413f83c4.poster.avif?t=1774841385\" width=616 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2846220/extras/79e6785449adf7a4d178b47c413f83c4.webm?t=1774841385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You go to work, come home, and just sleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're living those exhausting days that wear your soul down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one day...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;――Welcome home!&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That gentle voice welcomes you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the never-ending &quot;Days with My Sister&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></